Don't mind my first PHP project. It's a simple landing page with admin/user capabilities (formerly known as DLi).

Functions:
- Registration (User & Admin)
- Registration - Email Verification
- Forgot Password (User & Admin)
- Sign In
- Sign In - Email Code Verification
- Welcome Modal - Complete Profile (New Users Only)
- Update Profile (User & Admin)
- Change Password (User & Admin)
- View/Clear Activity & Email Log within GroupID (Admin Only)
- Send Email
- Add New User within GroupID with user/admin option (Admin Only)
- Upload Image
- Edit Image (current image will be replaced and deleted in DB and directory)
- Delete User within GroupID - will also delete image in directory (Admin Only)
- Logout

Currently Logging:
- Registration
- Sign In
- Log Out
- Update Profile
- Add User
- Delete User
- Email

Pending:
- Search Function
- Internal-Messaging System
